post_text: Monticello was well-representing at the River Valley conference honor choir Oct. 7 in Tipton. Participants were Kendra Foust, Abby Wilson, Payton Jaeger, Rylee McBride, Caroline Olsen, Adele Hogan, Robby Holmes, Jeff Carlson, Chase Sternhagen, Ben Oswald, Grahm Schneiter, Gary Pasker and Levi Temple.

post_text: Congratulations to senior Robby Holmes for earning a spot in the IHSMA All-State Festival chorus! A special shoutout goes to junior Gary Pasker for getting a callback. Bravo, gentlemen!
